step_data.thought: Looking at the current state of the page, I can see I'm on the Integrations page and there's a dialog open for 'Magento Analytics user'. The dialog shows integration tokens but I don't see a 'Reauthorize' button in the dialog. Instead, I see a 'Done' button. This suggests that the previous action might have completed the reauthorization process or that we need to take a different approach. \n\nIn the main table, I can see that the 'Magento Analytics user' integration has a 'Reauthorize' link in the 'Activate' column. Since the goal is to retry data synchronization with the Magento Business Intelligence service, and this appears to be the Magento Analytics/Business Intelligence integration, I should click on the 'Reauthorize' link in the table to initiate the data synchronization retry. Let me close this dialog first by clicking the 'Done' button, and then I'll click on the 'Reauthorize' link.
